latestIgtvVideos.title: My stay experience at @tatsaraasa
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The word ‘TatSaraasa’ is derived from Sanskrit and means – 'that which is calm, charming & beautiful'
Perched within the periphery of the udaipur city on the bank of tranquil lake lakhawali and encompassed by divine aravalli ranges.
Tatsarassa is truly a reason enough to be away from the city hustle and a perfect holiday getaway close in nature 🤍
